---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Investment Strategy">
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<span class="eyebrow">Investment Focus</span>
			<h1>Disciplined Capital for Defence and Defence-Adjacent Sectors</h1>
			<p>Strengthening NATO capabilities and Europe's technological sovereignty through investments in profitable, revenue-generating companies or those with secured commitments.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="thesis">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header text-center">
				<span class="eyebrow">Investment Thesis</span>
				<h2>Structural Drivers of <span class="outline">Defence</span></h2>
				<p class="section-subtitle">Artemis invests in European defence and dual-use technology companies positioned to benefit from the structural rearmament of Europe and the rapid expansion of defence industrial capacity.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-4 thesis-grid">
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">01</span>
					<h4>Structural Growth in Defence Spending</h4>
					<p>European defence budgets are increasing rapidly as NATO commitments rise and nations prioritize national security infrastructure.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">02</span>
					<h4>Technology Transformation of Warfare</h4>
					<p>Modern defence increasingly relies on electronic warfare, satellites, AI, and autonomous systems, necessitating rapid technological deployment.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">03</span>
					<h4>European Strategic Autonomy</h4>
					<p>EU and NATO are prioritizing domestic defence capabilities and resilient supply chains to ensure long-term technological sovereignty.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="thesis-card">
					<div class="card-glow"></div>
					<span class="card-num">04</span>
					<h4>Industrial Capacity Gap</h4>
					<p>European supply chains must scale quickly to support modern defence systems, creating significant opportunities for industrial expansion.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="criteria">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header">
				<span class="eyebrow">Investment Criteria</span>
				<h2>What We <span class="outline-dark">Look For</span></h2>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2 criteria-grid">
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Defence Sector Focus</h4>
					<p>Investments in companies operating in core defence and defence-adjacent markets across Europe, including cybersecurity, modern-warfare, spacecom, and adjacent sectors.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Established Operations</h4>
					<p>Targets profitable businesses with secured government or commercial contracts - revenue-generating companies or those with secured commitments.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Active Ownership</h4>
					<p>Majority positions with hands-on operational support from experienced C-level executives, ensuring alignment and accountability at every stage.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="criteria-item">
					<h4>Institutional Governance</h4>
					<p>Applying institutional standards, transparency, and best practices to portfolio management - building credibility with stakeholders and investors.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="strategy-details">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2">
				<div class="params">
					<h2>Investment Parameters</h2>
					<div class="param-item">
						<span class="label">Equity Ticket</span>
						<span class="value">€3M - €10M</span>
					</div>
					<div class="param-item">
						<span class="label">Holding Period</span>
						<span class="value">3 - 7 Years</span>
					</div>
					<div class="param-item">
						<span class="label">Stage</span>
						<span class="value">Growth & Scale-up</span>
					</div>
					<div class="param-item">
						<span class="label">Ownership</span>
						<span class="value">Controlling or Minority Stakes</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="sectors">
					<h2>Sector Focus</h2>
					<ul class="sector-list">
						<li>
							<span class="sector-num">01</span>
							<span class="sector-title">Defence Components</span>
							<span class="sector-sub">Critical Enablers & Supply Chain</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="sector-num">02</span>
							<span class="sector-title">Modern Warfare Systems</span>
							<span class="sector-sub">C4ISR, UAS & Autonomous Platforms</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="sector-num">03</span>
							<span class="sector-title">Cyber Security</span>
							<span class="sector-sub">Offensive & Defensive Capabilities</span>
						</li>
						<li>
							<span class="sector-num">04</span>
							<span class="sector-title">Space & Satcom</span>
							<span class="sector-sub">Space Situational Awareness</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="process">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="section-header text-center">
				<span class="eyebrow">Disciplined Process</span>
				<h2>Value <span class="outline">Creation</span></h2>
				<p class="section-subtitle">A systematic approach to identifying, scaling, and realizing value in defense technology.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-5 process-grid">
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-content">
						<span class="num">01</span>
						<h4>Sourcing</h4>
						<p>Leveraging our deep-tech network and proprietary industry outreach to identify mission-critical ventures.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-content">
						<span class="num">02</span>
						<h4>Due Diligence</h4>
						<p>Comprehensive technical, financial, and regulatory assessments followed by rigorous IC approval.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-content">
						<span class="num">03</span>
						<h4>Execution</h4>
						<p>Strategic transaction structuring focused on long-term alignment and technological sovereignty.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-content">
						<span class="num">04</span>
						<h4>Management</h4>
						<p>Active operational support and governance optimization, facilitating cross-border scale-up.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="step-content">
						<span class="num">05</span>
						<h4>Exit</h4>
						<p>Strategic value realization through global industry consolidators or public capital markets.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header { padding-top: 12rem; padding-bottom: 6rem; background: var(--color-secondary); color: var(--color-primary); }

	.page-header .eyebrow {
		display: block;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.25em;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		opacity: 0.6;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
		max-width: 700px;
	}

	.criteria {
		padding: 8rem 0;
		background: var(--color-primary);
	}

	.criteria .section-header { margin-bottom: 4rem; }

	.criteria h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	.outline-dark {
		color: transparent;
		-webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--color-secondary);
	}

	.criteria-grid { gap: 1.5rem; }

	.criteria-item {
		padding: 2.5rem;
		border: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.08);
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.3);
		transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
	}

	.criteria-item:hover {
		border-color: rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.2);
	}

	.criteria-item h4 {
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1rem;
	}

	.criteria-item p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		opacity: 0.65;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.strategy-details { padding: 10rem 0; }
	
	.params h2, .sectors h2 { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
	.param-item { margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.1); }
	.param-item .label { display: block; font-size: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.5; text-transform: uppercase; }
	.param-item .value { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 600; }

	.sector-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
	.sector-list li { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 1rem; padding: 1.25rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.1); flex-wrap: wrap; }
	.sector-num { font-family: monospace; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-secondary); opacity: 0.3; flex-shrink: 0; }
	.sector-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
	.sector-sub { font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; opacity: 0.45; }

	.thesis {
		padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
	}

	.thesis-grid { gap: 1.5rem; }

	.thesis-card {
		position: relative;
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.4);
		border: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.05);
		transition: all 0.4s ease;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.thesis-card:hover {
		border-color: rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.2);
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.6);
	}

	.card-glow {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		right: 0;
		width: 100px;
		height: 100px;
		background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.05), transparent 70%);
		opacity: 0;
		transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
	}

	.thesis-card:hover .card-glow { opacity: 1; }

	.card-num {
		font-family: monospace;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		opacity: 0.2;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.thesis-card h4 {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
		min-height: 3rem;
	}

	.thesis-card p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		opacity: 0.5;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	.section-subtitle {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 2rem auto 0;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		opacity: 0.6;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.grid-cols-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.grid-cols-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
		.thesis { padding: 8rem 0; }
	}

	.process {
		padding: 10rem 0; 
		background: #0d121c; 
		background-image: 
			radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.05) 1px, transparent 0);
		background-size: 40px 40px;
	}

	.section-header { margin-bottom: 6rem; }
	.eyebrow { 
		display: block; 
		text-transform: uppercase; 
		letter-spacing: 0.2em; 
		font-size: 0.8rem; 
		margin-bottom: 1rem; 
		opacity: 0.6;
	}
	.section-subtitle { 
		max-width: 600px; 
		margin: 2rem auto 0; 
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.outline { color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--color-secondary); }
	
	.process-grid { 
		gap: 1rem; 
		position: relative;
	}
	.step { 
		position: relative;
		padding: 2rem; 
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.5);
		border: 1px solid rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.1);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		z-index: 1;
	}
	
	/* Connector lines for desktop */
	@media (min-width: 1025px) {
		.step:not(:last-child)::after {
			content: '';
			position: absolute;
			top: 50%;
			right: -0.5rem;
			width: 1rem;
			height: 1px;
			background: rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.1);
			z-index: -1;
		}
	}
	.step:hover {
		border-color: rgba(238, 234, 225, 0.3);
		background: rgba(24, 33, 50, 0.8);
		transform: translateY(-5px);
	}

	.num { 
		font-family: monospace; 
		color: var(--color-secondary);
		opacity: 0.3; 
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem; 
		display: block; 
		font-size: 1.5rem;
	}
	.step h4 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-secondary); }
	.step p { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.6; line-height: 1.5; }

	@media (max-width: 1024px) {
		.process-grid {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.process-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.step {
			padding: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
